&lt;p&gt;
13-MXS clean room air slide tables, rated for contamination  grade 3, are great for applications that call for precise movement ranging from 10-150mm typically requiring a cylinder and precision guide.  The MXS is available in 6 bore sizes, each with set stroke lengths and is standard with auto-switch capability.  
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;P&gt;SMC&apos;s clean room version of the CXS dual rod cylinder is available in 6 bore sizes (6, 10, 16, 20, 25 and 32mm)&#xa0;with stroke lengths up to 100mm.&#xa0;It is suited for accurate pick-and-place applications or light duty material handling.&#xa0; The CXSJ, compact, dual rod cylinder is available in 2 bore sizes (6mm and 10mm) with strokes up to 50mm.&#xa0; Both the CXS and the CXSJ&#xa0;can be used with either reed or solid state switches. &lt;/P&gt;
